      "type": "NORMAL",
      "data": [
        {
          "value":
              "• • Children acquire language through communicative interactions between them and their environments\n• do not necessarily deny innateness, but only regard them as a last resort\n• believe in a set of general cognitive principles & predispositions to learn instead of UG"
        }
      ]
